      <container name="Recordando" eId="container_2">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="italic">Recordando</span> sus anteriores resoluciones relativas al Sudán, en particular las resoluciones <a href="https://undocs.org/sp/S/RES/1591(2005)">1591 (2005)</a>, <a href="https://undocs.org/sp/S/RES/1651(2005)">1651 (2005)</a>, <a href="https://undocs.org/sp/S/RES/1665(2006)">1665 (2006)</a>, <a href="https://undocs.org/sp/S/RES/1672(2006)">1672 (2006)</a>, <a href="https://undocs.org/sp/S/RES/1713(2006)">1713 (2006)</a>, <a href="https://undocs.org/sp/S/RES/1779(2007)">1779 (2007)</a>, <a href="https://undocs.org/sp/S/RES/1841(2008)">1841 (2008)</a>, <a href="https://undocs.org/sp/S/RES/1891(2009)">1891 (2009)</a>, <a href="https://undocs.org/sp/S/RES/1945(2010)">1945 (2010)</a>, <a href="https://undocs.org/sp/S/RES/1982(2011)">1982 (2011)</a>, <a href="https://undocs.org/sp/S/RES/2035(2012)">2035 (2012)</a>, <a href="https://undocs.org/sp/S/RES/2091(2013)">2091 (2013)</a>, <a href="https://undocs.org/sp/S/RES/2138(2014)">2138 (2014)</a>, <a href="https://undocs.org/sp/S/RES/2200(2015)">2200 (2015)</a>, <a href="https://undocs.org/sp/S/RES/2265(2016)">2265 (2016)</a>, <a href="https://undocs.org/sp/S/RES/2340(2017)">2340 (2017)</a>, <a href="https://undocs.org/sp/S/RES/2400(2018)">2400 (2018)</a> y <a href="https://undocs.org/sp/S/RES/2455(2019)">2455 (2019)</a>, y la declaración de su Presidencia de fecha 11 de diciembre de 2018 (<a href="https://undocs.org/sp/S/PRST/2018/19">S/PRST/2018/19</a>),</p>
      </container>
      <container name="Determinando" eId="container_3">
          <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="italic">Determinando</span> que la situación imperante en el Sudán sigue constituyendo una amenaza para la paz y la seguridad internacionales en la región,</p>
      </container>
      <container name="Recordando" eId="container_4">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="italic">Recordando</span> el informe final del Grupo de Expertos sobre el Sudán (<a href="https://undocs.org/sp/S/2020/36">S/</a><a href="https://undocs.org/sp/S/2020/36">2020/36</a>),</p>
      </container>
      <container name="Actuando" eId="container_5">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="italic">Actuando</span> en virtud del Capítulo VII de la Carta de las Naciones Unidas,</p>
      </container>
